the coloborators in your team.

93
00:04:52,671 --> 00:04:55,649
If you click on the tables logo,
you will land on the home screen.

94
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:58,000
Here you can find your bases.

95
00:04:58,050 --> 00:04:59,142
In my case, I have two.

96
00:04:59,529 --> 00:05:01,457
You can add more
bases with this button.

97
00:05:01,963 --> 00:05:04,410
One extra option that
we have here is templates.

98
00:05:05,476 --> 00:05:09,013
There are templates for many use
cases on this section that Zoho included.

99
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:11,615
So you don't have to start
building bases from scratch.

100
